-- mentions him as "eight years old" which would place birth in late 1960/early 1961.
-- However, velhosmestres.com explicitly states Sept 7, 1950 on the Gato Preto page.
-- Using 1950 with 'exact' precision (day-month-year confirmed).
--
-- APELIDO VARIATIONS:
-- - "Gato II" - most common, used in family/capoeira context
-- - "Mestre Góes" - used professionally at USP/ASSEBA
