  -- notes (researcher metadata)
  E'BIRTH YEAR ESTIMATION (1970, decade):
No birth date found in sources. Father Mestre Baiano was born August 30, 1945. Grandão trained "from childhood" and participated in Rio hotel shows, took break at 15, returned at 19. First Europe trip at 21 with father. Assuming childhood training began age 5-8, places birth in late 1960s to early 1970s.

NAME: "Antonio Marcos dos A. Reis" - sources consistently use this form; full middle name unclear (likely "Anjos" based on father''s documented variations as "Antonio Marcos dos Anjos Reis").

