-- early 1970s. Born on Ilha de Bom Jesus dos Passos near Salvador,
-- he trained under Mestre Pelé da Bomba and founded Grupo de
-- Capoeira Oxóssi (1968). He developed "Capoeira de Rua" with
-- Angolan foundation and is famous for his "chapa da morte" kick.
--
-- BIRTH YEAR ESTIMATION:
-- Primary source (capoeiradomercado.com) states July 26, 1950,
-- born on Ilha de Bom Jesus dos Passos. Other sources say 1955
