-- ============================================================
-- GENEALOGY PERSON: Ivan de Santo Amaro
-- Generated: 2026-01-11
-- ============================================================
-- BIRTH YEAR ESTIMATION (1966, year precision):
-- Velhosmestres.com states "M Ivan started training with Ferreirinha in 1976
-- at the age of ten." This gives birth year of ~1966.
