-- - Teacher Inauá (estimated birth ~1940) would have been training students by 1970s
-- - King Kong participated in Quinta da Boa Vista rodas (famous in 1950s-1970s)
-- - If he participated as an adult (20-30 years old) in the 1970s, birth ~1950-1960
-- - Student Baia founded Geração Nagô in 2013; if Baia was 30-40, born ~1973-1983
-- - King Kong training Baia in ~1990s as established mestre (age 35-45) suggests birth ~1950-1960
