CONTEMPORARIES:
- Rosa Palmeirão (shares chapter in Pedro Abib''s book)
- Salomé (student of Doze Homens)
- Chicão (Francisca Albino dos Santos) - killed Pedro Porreta
- Maria Doze Homens
- Angélica Endiabrada (1910-1920)
- Catu (Antônia de Tal)
- Almerinda
- Menininha

CHAPTER TITLE: "Rosa Palmeirão e Massú: Vacila pra tu vê!" - The phrase suggests a reputation for quick, decisive retaliation when challenged.

DOCUMENTATION:
Limited documentation available beyond mentions in lists of legendary valentonas and the chapter title in Pedro Abib''s work. No specific incidents, police records, or newspaper accounts found. Full name unknown.',
  E'ESTIMATIVA DO ANO DE NASCIMENTO (1895, década):
Contemporânea de Rosa Palmeirão (ativa ~1910s), Chicão (ativa 1920s-30s), Salomé (ativa 1920s-30s). Se no auge (25-35 anos) durante 1910s-1920s, nascimento ~1880-1900. Usando 1895 como ponto médio.

MESTRES:
