BRAZILIAN BOXING FEDERATION RECOGNITION:
The 1973 mestre recognition from the Confederação Brasileira de Pugilismo (now Boxe) reflects the period when capoeira was administratively under boxing federations. The Brazilian Capoeira Confederation (CBC) was later founded in 1993 to establish autonomous governance.

PROFESSIONAL LIFE:
- Education: Business Administration (UNISUAM - Sociedade Universitária Augusto Motta)
- Profession: Work Safety Technologist (Tecnólogo em Segurança do Trabalho)
- Residence: Parada de Lucas, Rio de Janeiro

IPHAN REGISTRY:
Updated February 10, 2019. Registered as "Mestre Rui Henrique" with style listed as "Capoeira" (generic). Instructor since 1969. Participated in "Mais Educação" social education project.

MÁRIO BUSCAPÉ REFERENCE:
The Capoeira History article mentions Mário Buscapé (Mário Santos), founder of the Bonfim group, as a "key reference" for understanding capoeira lineage in Rio. This suggests Mário Buscapé''s influence on the broader Rio capoeira scene rather than direct teacher-student relationship with Rui Henrique.',
  E'DATA DE NASCIMENTO: 19 de agosto de 1950 (confirmado pelo registro do IPHAN)

PROFESSOR:
- Mestre Zé Maria (José Maria da Silva): Professor principal; treinou no Grupo Império da Tijuca (a partir de 1968)

ALUNOS:
