- Mestre João Valença
- Mestre Barreto

CONTRA-MESTRE TITLE:
Granted in 1950s by Mestre João Grande. Locally known as "João Bate-Estaca" in Ilhéus region. João Grande was born in nearby Itagi, southern Bahia.

ORGANIZATIONS FOUNDED:
